You're okay?

47:52.480 --> 47:53.920
You're okay! You're--

47:53.960 --> 47:56.800
I'm okay. I'm fine.

47:56.840 --> 47:59.400
♪ Got the music
in you, baby ♪

47:59.440 --> 48:00.600
♪ Tell me why

48:00.640 --> 48:02.280
I love you.

48:02.320 --> 48:04.760
I love you, too.

48:04.800 --> 48:07.880
♪ And you just
can't say goodbye ♪

48:07.920 --> 48:10.720
[Fern laughs]

48:10.760 --> 48:12.600
Come here. Ha ha!

48:12.640 --> 48:14.720
♪ Kisses on the foreheads

48:14.760 --> 48:18.640
♪ Of the lovers
wrapped in your arms ♪

48:21.440 --> 48:23.840
♪ You've been hiding them

48:23.880 --> 48:27.080
♪ In hollowed out pianos
left in the dark ♪

48:27.120 --> 48:28.600
Does your boat
ever leave the dock?

48:32.400 --> 48:34.600
Well, yes.

48:34.640 --> 48:37.800
I mean, I've been
preoccupied lately.

48:37.840 --> 48:40.000
♪ Got the music
in you, baby ♪

48:40.040 --> 48:42.760
But now I have
to take time off,

48:44.320 --> 48:45.840
so maybe...

48:47.280 --> 48:48.640
the Whitsundays?

48:50.200 --> 48:52.280
There's room.

48:52.320 --> 48:53.840
I can't take time off.

48:56.080 --> 48:57.920
I need to do well
at my job.

48:57.960 --> 48:59.520
I can't fail again.

49:01.440 --> 49:03.560
I don't think you ever failed.

49:03.600 --> 49:07.040
I think you were just finding
where you needed to be.

49:07.080 --> 49:10.040
♪ Apocalypse

49:13.360 --> 49:15.760
♪ Go and sneak us
through the rivers ♪

49:15.800 --> 49:19.440
♪ Flood is rising up
on your knees ♪

49:19.480 --> 49:23.280
Technically,
I'm still suspended.

49:24.600 --> 49:26.680
So, technically...

49:27.920 --> 49:29.360
You're not my supervisor.

49:31.120 --> 49:32.400
Ohh.

49:33.680 --> 49:35.720
♪ Sharing all your secrets

49:35.760 --> 49:39.640
♪ With each other
since you were kids ♪

49:39.680 --> 49:43.040
But that won't
last long, will it?

49:43.080 --> 49:45.600
♪ Sleeping soundly
with the locket ♪

49:45.640 --> 49:47.560
See you back at work
in a couple of weeks.

49:47.600 --> 49:50.120
♪ Clutched in your fist

49:53.480 --> 49:55.960
♪ Got the music
in you, baby ♪

49:56.000 --> 49:58.560
♪ Tell me why

