50:17.840 --> 50:19.200
Harrow.

50:21.520 --> 50:24.920
[suspenseful music]

50:27.200 --> 50:28.960
[police radio chatter]

50:39.840 --> 50:41.840
You do understand
I'm on leave at the moment?

50:41.880 --> 50:43.760
Sorry, Dr Harrow.
Nichols insisted.

50:53.000 --> 50:54.520
Nichols, what's going on?

50:54.560 --> 50:58.480
This young man was found dead
about an hour ago.

50:58.520 --> 51:00.200
What's it
got to do with me?

51:01.240 --> 51:03.160
Found his passport
in his pocket.

51:04.760 --> 51:07.480
Your name is down
as his emergency contact.

51:15.120 --> 51:16.960
And there was a note.

51:18.080 --> 51:19.840
He claimed he was your son.

51:19.880 --> 51:22.080
[ominous music]

